14 WHEREAS, the State of Oklahoma has a health care shortage, in
15 particular in the rural parts of the state; and
16 WHEREAS, the State of Oklahoma wants to support and protect the
17 rural health care community and medical care provided in those
18 areas; and
19 WHEREAS, the Physician Self-Referral Law or Stark Law, 42
20 U.S.C., Section 1395nn, within the Social Security Act of the United
21 States Code, is an impediment to the rural health care community and
22 medical care.
